{"tid":109507,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇錦樑回應美食車食物昂貴批評：市民排隊支持就是對價錢的肯定","createTime":"2017-02-06T04:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T08:30:47.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09b9e79e329f5059ba82b7118d82a90df169ab5e","tid":109507,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:18:36.000Z","msg":"美食車先導計劃的首批11架車，已經於前日開始營業，雖然吸引不少人排隊，但就有人批評價錢昂貴。 商務及經濟發展局局長蘇錦樑今日（2月5日）出席公開場合後，指從排隊的人數上可以看到，無論旅客或市民，都覺得這些美食非常吸引，相信他們排隊支持，已表示他們對價錢的肯定。蘇錦樑又相信營運者會因應市場的需要作出調整，但就強調是他們自己的決定。 蘇錦樑又提到，在剛過去的年三十至年初六，中國訪港旅客增長了6.6%，整體旅客數字增長了5.1%，跟去年中國旅客數字下降12.1%，是一個很大的對比。他希望與業界一起共同努力，透過引入美食車、盛事和其他特色文化旅遊項目，豐富旅遊內容，期望能夠吸引更多旅客來港。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;"},{"pid":"fc905608203fefc4be14cc5bf9d5ff0a2f176fd8","tid":109507,"uid":30644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/06/123148_bda00f79ab029612ff2edd949bffd999.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F06%2F123148_bda00f79ab029612ff2edd949bffd999.jpg&h=15e22aef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b497ee17b460bedbd86642354764bb67ce375d0","tid":109507,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:41:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/06/123148_bda00f79ab029612ff2edd949bffd999.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F06%2F123148_bda00f79ab029612ff2edd949bffd999.jpg&h=15e22aef&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8790a87f7ca34ebadb2ac87dc2fa8e637e9464","tid":109507,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:10:07.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得價錢算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n始終佢target係遊客 唔通set個地踎價錢咩"},{"pid":"d58872b70b7dd5d93d8ee4f